#Text=Find Your Calling in Life
#Text=We all search for our calling , even though we speak it in It our heads we are still looking for it .
#Text=It may be different for us all .
#Text=It could be loosing weight for one and maybe gaining it after some terrible disease for another .
#Text=I may be being a motivational speaker for one and practising meditation in an alone place for another .
#Text=Here you will get a little direction to what your must do , to find yours .
#Text=Steps
#Text=Look into the mirror .
#Text=Look into the mirror and you will see someone who has come here for a purpose .
#Text=You are witnessing the one who has the potential to change the world , to make a difference here and you could be starting from this very moment .
#Text=You can make this day count , you can make your life count and it begins today .
#Text=Smile ... something great is upcoming
#Text=Pick up a diary .
#Text=Leave the initial few pages blank and write down point by point , all you want to " BE " .
#Text=All you want to have may have a very long list but all you want to be would sum up in around 2 pages .
#Text=You might want to be funny , charming , loved , confidant , intelligent , puntual , preety , stylish , polite , fit , brave .
#Text=Not everybody wants the same things .
#Text=Keep this list safe , because now you have met yourself and expressed what you want to be .
#Text=Start planning out .
#Text=These diaries are going to be your friend for life if you let them be .

#Text=You now have an idea of what you want to become , so start looking up in books , internet , right people from whom you will get ideas so that you can map out your day in such a manner that you start to approach your targets in small but meaningful steps each day .
#Text=Once you are done with the plan execute it for a week .
#Text=See how it goes , then make the necessary changes .

#Text=Your week could have stuff planned like 30 min of cardio+ 1 hr reading a motivational book+ 15 min of gratitude(V.V.Important)+8hours of work+1 hour of playing the piano/cooking/vocabulary/Enhancing your body language skills/Lerning about dresses and the list goes on .
#Text=Calling involves being of value .
#Text=What you possibly might have skipped out of your list would be making your life more meaningful .
#Text=In order to get , give. .
#Text=The people who found their purpose had two things in common , one they were grateful and values their lives and second they gave something back to the world .
#Text=Mother teresa , Oprah Winfrey , Anjelina Jolie , Nelson Mandela , Abraham Lincon , they all has this in common and so can you .
#Text=Discipline is the key to achieve it .
#Text=It may look hard initially when you begin the journey .
#Text=you might wanna just stop and take the long rest , but be disciplined with your efforts and flexible with your methods .
#Text=You have to know , that with the effort that you are looking for your calling in life , it i looking for you too .
#Text=Try this for a month
#Text=Plan your days , set up weekly tasks and try this for a month .
#Text=You will get to know yourself better , you will become better and stronger with each step you take .
